{"tid":52633,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"powerbeats 3開箱","createTime":"2016-12-24T08:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T15:53:00.000Z","uid":6164,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb9ddd6413f622f56a8a4e80f33b4b3b2460b138","tid":52633,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/155348_86c6c0c43642403b5a3d963edde036ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F155348_86c6c0c43642403b5a3d963edde036ce.jpg&h=d8ed41ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66b0q87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66b0q87.jpg&h=4e5fe6ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/155349_e60863ef2df5981a447d9b391919484a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F155349_e60863ef2df5981a447d9b391919484a.jpg&h=3fc9babf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5am3wOB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5am3wOB.jpg&h=d0dd4a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hT25Ft9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhT25Ft9.jpg&h=264f9a8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇防水蓋，不過個充電口向下，落雨冇乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rjg33NA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frjg33NA.jpg&h=f7f2f40f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n得一粒指示燈，有w1晶片，靠近iPhone一開就配對<br />\n<br />\n咁第一次就要靠近iPhone配對， 詳情同airpods一樣唔講啦。但係一離開咗配對範圍，個耳機同手機斷左線後，只要個耳機係iPhone隔離禁個耳機嘅開關掣，就會立即配對返，幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/155731_b0bf822282e6f50c062a4eb23a50f6fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F155731_b0bf822282e6f50c062a4eb23a50f6fc.jpg&h=b207578a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/155732_c9fb6bc0951e9b0982900a3a612e1deb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F155732_c9fb6bc0951e9b0982900a3a612e1deb.jpg&h=08ac7f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個附送嘅耳機套冇拉鍊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/155816_4078439cedf379652cb3075e8befb318.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F155816_4078439cedf379652cb3075e8befb318.jpg&h=85ec99a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個尾有個扣<br />\n<br />\n總結，聽歌質素一定好過airpods,但係通話收音質素airpods好小小，powerbeats聽歌時間12個鐘多少少，Airpods就五個鐘多少少。powerbeats 有快差，差5分鐘可以聽一個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n雖然Powerbeats3比airpods重，但係帶上去又唔覺得會墜落去，嗰個耳掛唔使掂住耳仔都唔會跌，所以我覺得唔使擔心重量問題。<br />\n<br />\n結論就係，我覺得Powerbeats3好好多，唯一唔好係多條線，唔係真無線。價錢都係貴200蚊到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d300f67127fc719ba87b94a1f083099be73506","tid":52633,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:12:20.000Z","msg":"考慮咗好耐先捨棄airpods<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1b6573cbca81dda12691aee745669782986cfe","tid":52633,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:14:23.000Z","msg":"有個2<br />\n<br />\n3 代好似大改得好勁<br />\n正"},{"pid":"6bea13b8a15948ef14f25c2ae52e20c31401ceef","tid":52633,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個2<br />\n<br />\n3 代好似大改得好勁<br />\n正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n3帶得舒服左，啲聲音比第二代平衡<br />\n<br />\n但係紅色個樣冇第二代咁靚，個耳機套唔識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7957c6a5a5227dde18cd1f8336716bc625eefe56","tid":52633,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:37:01.000Z","msg":"邊到買最平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1221f4ffcf8696565fcf7d1a14661a8c885f346a","tid":52633,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:41:48.000Z","msg":"用左24小時，冇斷過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02869bc0b7891fbb228255de96798ff50ffd0c9","tid":52633,"uid":12190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:59:01.000Z","msg":"等緊beatsx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0808c2ba4ee51659b0349a07e2c77c864f96b2d0","tid":52633,"uid":25721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T09:02:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾牌子"},{"pid":"06d1191f85afaeb68f074d7d2aa94400b1504d89","tid":52633,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T09:06:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等緊beatsx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cf7e45133a941136d940ff